{
  "chapter": 27,
  "chapter_summary": "第二十七回「自裁以谢」。无花微笑与楚留香论法，言称宁死不愿受卑贱之人审判，随即服毒自尽。楚留香大恸，抱无花尸身至林家花园，告知秃鹰与丐帮长老凶手已死。丐帮长老追问尸身下落，被楚留香暴怒斥责。楚留香因无花之死悲痛疲倦，独自赶回船上，途中遇平生未有的惊人变故。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "无花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "无论如何，你这种观念的确是令人佩服的，自古以来，江湖中只怕谁也没有这样想过。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_wu_hua",
      "text": "等到许多年以后，这样想的人，自然会一天天多起来，以后人们自然会知道，武功并不能解决一切，世上没有一个人有权力夺去别人的生命!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "无花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "这是以后的事了，现在你……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_wu_hua",
      "text": "现在，我要将你交给能制裁你的人手上。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "无花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你要将我交给别人?",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_wu_hua",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "无花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你既不能制裁我，天下还有谁能制裁我?",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_wu_hua",
      "text": "他们这些人，虽然未见得如何高尚，但他们所代表的法律和规矩，却是无论什么人都须尊敬的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "无花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你难道一向很尊重规矩?",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_wu_hua",
      "text": "我们蔑视的，只是少数人立下的规矩，这种规矩自然不值得尊敬，但道德和正义，无论任何人也不该轻视。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "无花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "楚留香，你实在是个很奇怪的人，但你无论如何，也休想将我交到那种人手上。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_wu_hua",
      "text": "为什么?你本是个很高贵的人，那些人的手本不敢沾着你的衣衫，但又谁叫你犯了如此卑下的罪，'王子犯法，与民同罪'，这句话你难道不懂?",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "无花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "楚留香，无论如何，你也休想要那种人沾着我的一根手指。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_wu_hua",
      "text": "无花，你……你为何这样笨!死，难道就不可逃避么?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "无花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我这并不是逃避，我并不是不敢去面对他们，我只不过是不屑在那种卑贱的人面前低头而已。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "无花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "无论我做错了什么事，我总是高贵的人，比世上大多数人都要高贵得多!楚留香，这点你承认么?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gai_bang_zhang_lao",
      "speaker_name": "丐帮长老",
      "listener": "char_tu_ying",
      "text": "你想他真的会来么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "秃鹰",
      "listener": "char_gai_bang_zhang_lao",
      "text": "无论楚留香这人是好是坏，是善是恶，但他既说要来，就一定会来，无论什么人，什么事，都休想挡得住他。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_tu_ying",
      "text": "不错，无论秃鹰这人是好是坏，是善是恶，但他对楚留香的看法，倒是不错的……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_tu_ying",
      "text": "但秃鹰是不是已听到我在树上，才故意说这些话的?",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "秃鹰",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "楚香帅一诺千金，是小老儿早已知道的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gai_bang_zhang_lao",
      "speaker_name": "丐帮长老",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "那凶手不知楚香帅已带回来了么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_gai_bang_zhang_lao",
      "text": "他已死了!",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "秃鹰",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "死了?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_tu_ying",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "秃鹰",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "他……他是如何死的?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_tu_ying",
      "text": "他既已死了，无论是怎样死的，岂非都是一样么?",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "秃鹰",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "但……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_tu_ying",
      "text": "我说他死了，你难道还不信?",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "秃鹰",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "楚香帅的话，小老儿怎敢不信?但他……他究竟是谁呢?",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_tu_ying",
      "text": "他虽然狠毒，但却并不卑鄙，他虽是个凶手，但却仍不失为君子，现在，他既已死了，你们何苦再问他姓名，人一死，就没有名字了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gai_bang_zhang_lao",
      "speaker_name": "丐帮长老",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "但他的尸身在哪里?他就算死了，本帮弟子也要想办法将他的尸身……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_gai_bang_zhang_lao",
      "text": "你要将他的尸身怎样?你竟想去对付一个死人，这想法岂非比那凶手还要卑鄙得多!",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我告诉你他已死了，他的死，已洗清了他生前的罪，你们若不信，你们若还不满意，只管自己去法子吧!但你们若再敢来打扰我，休怪我不客气!",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    }
  ],
